cs.LG, cs.IT, cs.CY, cs.CR, cs.AI

The paper discusses the cost-benefit analysis of data intelligence workflows, which is a topic related to machine learning and information theory. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.IT (Information Theory), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are likely sub-categories. The paper also discusses encryption and compression, which are related to cybersecurity, making cs.CY (Cryptography and Security) a possible sub-category. Finally, the paper discusses perception, cognition, languages, and news media, which are related to human-computer interaction and natural language processing, making cs.CR (Human-Computer Interaction) a possible sub-category.
